# Plan Execution Completion Tracking

When executing a plan set from `.llm/plans/active/**`:

1. Execute numbered plan files in the order defined by `00-EXECUTION-ORDER.md` and `COPY-PASTA.md`.
2. After each completed numbered prompt, update `COPY-PASTA.md` to mark that prompt as completed.
3. Move each completed numbered plan file from `active/` to the mirrored `completed/` directory path.
4. Keep `COPY-PASTA.md` and `00-*` files in `active/` until all numbered prompts are complete.
5. When all numbered prompts are complete, move the remaining plan-set files and directory to `completed/`.

This tracking is required for plan implementation responses so progress is durable and visible.
